    "text": "Flexibility in Addressing Rural Homelessness Act of 2022\n\nThis bill allows grants awarded under the ongoing Continuum of Care program to include grants for projects in rural areas for short-term emergency lodging; repairs to unfit housing for homeless individuals; and staff training, development, and retention."
